Short description:
About the Food Processor FP 190

If you like to keep things simple, this food processor is just the job for preparing small amounts of vegetables and other ingredients for everyday cooking.

Practical

The Food Processor FP 190 has a white and grey finish and comes with a 600W motor, 1.4 litre bowl with 800ml working capacity, and a great range of attachments for chopping and grating vegetables. There's a 1 litre blender for drinks, soups, sauces and smoothies. Plus a citrus press for making delicious breakfast juices any time of the day.

Quick and simple

This useful kitchen accessory will quickly take care of all those slicing, chopping, whisking, grating, juicing and blending tasks, so that you have more time to cook and serve great food. The sharp, stainless steel blade will cut through those little everyday preparation jobs in no time. There is a safety interlock to make sure the motor doesn't start until the bowl lid is firmly fixed in place.

Name: SM-640
Short description:
About the Kenwood Sandwich Maker SM 640

Safety latch ensure toaster stays closed when in use

Convenient, quick and easy to use

there's so much you can do with the white Kenwood Sandwich Maker SM640. From tasty cheese toasties, sandwich melts and panini, experiment with different fillings for your perfect toasted sandwich. Grill vegetables and kebabs for healthy nutritious meals. Make sweet snacks and desserts such as pancakes and fruit turnovers. And for savory snacks and meals try omelets, calzones and crispy burritos.

Versatility

The 700W Kenwood SM640 Sandwich Maker has capacity for two rounds of sandwiches / four slices. It comes with two sets of removable cooking plates - triangle sandwich plates and grill/griddle plates - designed to toast, grill and griddle a variety of foods. The plates are non-stick coated so that food can easily be served and for easy cleaning. There are plate release catches and the plates have handles on each side for better handling.

Simplicity

A safety latch ensures the sandwich toaster remains closed when in use and rubberized feet ensure it stays in one place. When in use as a griddle, it opens flat for ease of cooking. There are 'on / off' and 'ready' neon indicators to show the power state of the sandwich maker and when it is ready to start cooking. And ergonomically-designed carrying handles make the Kenwood Sandwich Maker SM640 easy to move and store in the kitchen.

Name: SM-650
Short description:
About the Kenwood Sandwich Maker SM 650

Convenient, quick and easy to use, there's so much you can do with the white Kenwood Sandwich Maker SM650. From tasty cheese toasties, sandwich melts and panini, experiment with different fillings for your perfect toasted sandwich.

The white Kenwood Sandwich Maker SM 650.

Convenient, quick and easy to use, there's so much you can do with the white Kenwood Sandwich Maker SM650. From tasty cheese toasties, sandwich melts and panini, experiment with different fillings for your perfect toasted sandwich. Grill vegetables and kebabs for healthy nutritious meals. Make sweet snacks and desserts such as waffles, pancakes and fruit turnovers. And for savory snacks and meals try omelets, calzones and crispy burritos.

Versatility

The 700W Kenwood SM650 Sandwich Maker has capacity for two rounds of sandwiches / four slices. It comes with three sets of removable cooking plates - triangle sandwich plates, waffle plates, and grill/griddle plates - designed to toast, grill and griddle a variety of foods. The plates are non-stick coated so that food can easily be served and for easy cleaning. There are plate release catches and the plates have handles on each side for better handling.

Simplicity

A safety latch ensures the sandwich toaster remains closed when in use and rubberized feet ensure it stays in one place. When in use as a griddle, it opens flat for ease of cooking. There are 'on / off' and 'ready' neon indicators to show the power state of the sandwich maker and when it is ready to start cooking. And ergonomically-designed carrying handles make the Kenwood Sandwich Maker SM 650 easy to move and store in the kitchen.

Name: SM-740
Short description:
About the Kenwood Sandwich Maker SM 740

Convenient, quick and easy to use, there's so much you can do with the white Kenwood Sandwich Maker SM740. It is our largest and most powerful sandwich maker with a 1300W heating element and capacity for four rounds of sandwiches / eight slices.

Convenient, quick and easy to use

There's so much you can do with the white Kenwood Sandwich Maker SM 740. It is our largest and most powerful sandwich maker with a 1300W heating element and capacity for four rounds of sandwiches / eight slices. From tasty cheese toasties, sandwich melts and panini, experiment with different fillings for your perfect toasted sandwich. Grill vegetables and kebabs for healthy nutritious meals. Make sweet snacks and desserts such as pancakes and fruit turnovers. And for savory snacks and meals try omelets, calzones and crispy burritos.

Versatility

The Kenwood SM 740 Sandwich Maker comes with two sets of removable cooking plates - triangle sandwich plates and grill/griddle plates - designed to toast, grill and griddle a variety of foods. The plates are non-stick coated so that food can easily be served and for easy cleaning. There are plate release catches and the plates have handles on each side for better handling.

Simplicity

A safety latch ensures the sandwich toaster remains closed when in use and rubberized feet ensure it stays in one place. When in use as a griddle, it opens flat for ease of cooking and includes two oil drip trays. There are 'on / off' and 'ready' neon indicators to show the power state of the sandwich maker and when it is ready to start cooking. And ergonomically-designed carrying handles make the Kenwood Sandwich Maker SM 740 easy to move and store in the kitchen.

•  Power 700 W

  •  A safety latch ensures toaster stays closed when in use
  •  Open flat for using as a griddle
  •  Plate release button
  •  On-off and Ready neon indicators
  •  4 Slice, 2 in 1 sandwich with Grill
